    <h1>The terminal that lets Claude<br/>drive<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
    <p class="lede">A macOS terminal built around the Claude Code agent. Claude runs in a primary terminal and orchestrates the dev-server terminals around it — while you keep full visibility and can grab the wheel.</p>
    <div class="cta"><a class="btn primary" href="#install">Install with Homebrew</a><a class="btn" href="https://github.com/maw-sh/maw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">★ Star on GitHub</a></div>
    <div class="install" id="copyHero" style="margin-top:16px;width:max-content;max-width:100%;cursor:pointer"><span class="pr">$</span><span>brew install --cask maw-sh/maw/maw</span><span class="cp">copy</span></div>
  </div>
